      "span_text": "In order to correct this problem, according to [CITATION_1] , a modified matrix B called B* has been obtained by dividing the elements of each column by the element of the main diagonal and later on by eliminating the elements of the diagonal to avoid double accounting of the direct effect of its own innovation intensity:"
